<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.10.8">
<l>tāḻaitaṇ ṇāmpal taṭamperum poykaivāy</l>
<l>vāḻu mutalai valaippaṭṭu vātippuṇ</l>
<l>vēḻam tuyarkeṭa viṇṇōr perumāṉāy</l>
<l>āḻipaṇi koṇṭāṉā liṉṟumuṟṟum</l>
<l rend="indent">ataṟkaruḷ ceytāṉā liṉṟumuṟṟum.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having been caught in the crocodile’s trap</l>
<l rend="indent">in a huge, wide pool with cool water-lilies and screw-pine,</l>
<l>As the lord of celestials, he ended the suffering</l>
<l rend="indent">of the elephant who was experiencing [such] trouble,</l>
<l>Because of him who himself took on the service with [his] discus,</l>
<l rend="indent">now we’re at our end,</l>
<l>Because of him who granted grace to that [elephant],</l>
<l rend="indent">now we’re at our end</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
